		(uuid "af0f7717-6b56-4277-83d9-29ff39cb049a")
	)
	(text "As the LiPo battery voltage can drop below the desired system voltage of\n3.3 V, and because the input voltage can be as high as 5 V,\nuse a buck-boost regulator."
