	(text_box "Buck-Boost regulator with soft start\n\nThe regulator is capable of sourcing\n2 A @ V_{IN} = 3 V and 4 A @ V_{IN} = 5V.\n\nThe MCU drains about 100 mA in a worst case scenario.\nThe modem drains about 500 mA in a worst case scenario."
